Very nice little Indonesian Cafe in the middle of Down Town Miami.  We were there yesterday on a Sunday Afternoon and the food was great ! We did order the Rijsttafel. I ate in my life in a lot of So Called Indonesian Restaurants in the …

Stumbled on this hidden gem while walking around downtown today.  So glad we decided to stop in!  The food was amazing and the prices quite reasonable.  Really wish Miami had more Indonesian/Asian restaurants like this one.  Will definitely be returning!
Delicious food.  This is the place in Miami that I go to when I crave Indo food. Service is excellent. Nice gamelan music much like home. Love it.
Not a very large place, but it is clean and the food comes out pretty quick.  The food is good and the prices are relatively low.
